    <script type="text/javascript" language="javascript">
"use strict";

        /**
         * Taken from http://www.quirksmode.org/js/detect.html
         */
        var BrowserDetect = {
            init: function () {
                this.browser = this.searchString(this.dataBrowser) || "An unknown browser";
                this.version = this.searchVersion(navigator.userAgent)
                    || this.searchVersion(navigator.appVersion)
                    || "an unknown version";
                this.OS = this.searchString(this.dataOS) || "an unknown OS";
            },
            searchString: function (data) {
                for (var i = 0;i < data.length; i++) {
                    var dataString = data[i].string;
                    var dataProp = data[i].prop;
                    this.versionSearchString = data[i].versionSearch || data[i].identity;
                    if (dataString) {
                        if (dataString.indexOf(data[i].subString) != -1)
                            return data[i].identity;
                    }
                    else if (dataProp)
                        return data[i].identity;
                }
            },
            searchVersion: function (dataString) {
                var index = dataString.indexOf(this.versionSearchString);
                if (index == -1) return;
                return parseFloat(dataString.substring(index+this.versionSearchString.length+1));
            },
            dataBrowser: [
                /*****DO NOT MODIFY THE ORDER OF THE AGENTS LISTED HERE.***********
                **This is explained in the link at the top of the code (quirksmode)*/
                {
                    string: navigator.userAgent,
                    subString: "Chrome",
                    identity: "Chrome"
                },
                {   string: navigator.userAgent,
                    subString: "OmniWeb",
                    versionSearch: "OmniWeb/",
                    identity: "OmniWeb"
                },
                {
                    string: navigator.vendor,
                    subString: "Apple",
                    identity: "Safari",
                    versionSearch: "Version"
                },
                {
                    prop: window.opera,
                    identity: "Opera",
                    versionSearch: "Version"
                },
                {
                    string: navigator.vendor,
                    subString: "iCab",
                    identity: "iCab"
                },
                {
                    string: navigator.vendor,
                    subString: "KDE",
                    identity: "Konqueror"
                },
                {
                    string: navigator.userAgent,
                    subString: "Firefox",
                    identity: "Firefox"
                },
                {
                    string: navigator.vendor,
                    subString: "Camino",
                    identity: "Camino"
                },
                {       // for newer Netscapes (6+)
                    string: navigator.userAgent,
                    subString: "Netscape",
                    identity: "Netscape"
                },
                {
                    string: navigator.userAgent,
                    subString: "MSIE",
                    identity: "Explorer",
                    versionSearch: "MSIE"
                },
                {
                    string: navigator.userAgent,
                    subString: "Gecko",
                    identity: "Mozilla",
                    versionSearch: "rv"
                },
                {       // for older Netscapes (4-)
                    string: navigator.userAgent,
                    subString: "Mozilla",
                    identity: "Netscape",
                    versionSearch: "Mozilla"
                }
            ],
            dataOS : [
                {
                    string: navigator.platform,
                    subString: "Win",
                    identity: "Windows"
                },
                {
                    string: navigator.platform,
                    subString: "Mac",
                    identity: "Mac"
                },
                {
                    string: navigator.userAgent,
                    subString: "iPhone",
                    identity: "iPhone/iPod"
                },
                {
                    string: navigator.platform,
                    subString: "Linux",
                    identity: "Linux"
                }
            ]
        };
        BrowserDetect.init();

        var skipChecked = function() {
            var key, val, res;
            var allCookies = document.cookie.split(';');
            for(var i = 0;i<allCookies.length; i++) {
                key = decodeURIComponent(allCookies[i].substr(0,allCookies[i].indexOf("=")));
                val = decodeURIComponent(allCookies[i].substr(allCookies[i].indexOf("=")+1));
                if (key.replace(/(^\s+|\s+$)/g,"") == "COMPATIBILITY_WARNING") {
                    res = JSON.parse(val);
                    if (res.version === '10.2.0') {
                        return true;
                    }
                }
            }
            return false;
        };

        var checkIfPlatformCompatible = function() {
            if (!compatibleBrowser() && !skipChecked()) {
                window.open("compatibleBrowsers.html", "_parent");
            } else {
                window.open("login.jsp", "_parent");
            }
        };

        var compatibleBrowser = function() {
            if(BrowserDetect.OS === 'Mac') {
                if (BrowserDetect.browser === 'Safari' || BrowserDetect.version >= 6) {
                    return true;
                }
            } else if(BrowserDetect.browser === 'Firefox'  && BrowserDetect.version >= 25) {
                return true;
            } else if(['Explorer', 'Mozilla'].indexOf(BrowserDetect.browser) > -1 && BrowserDetect.version >= 9) {
                return true;
            } else if(BrowserDetect.browser === 'Chrome'   && BrowserDetect.version >= 30) {
                return true;
            }
            // Unsupported browser detected
            return false;
        }
    </script>
